    "By employing machine learning algorithms, LLMs can analyze patterns of reviewer preferences and past performances, optimizing the selection process and broadening the pool of available reviewers [24].",
    "Farber [25] reported a 42% overlap between GPT-4-suggested reviewers and those manually selected by editors and 37% additional qualified reviewers identified by GPT-4, who were not initially considered.",
    "Notably, GPT-4 reduced reviewer selection time by 73%, from 45 to 12 minutes, demonstrating its potential to improve efficiency and identify experts across diverse fields.",
